        "created_at": "2025-01-09T14:45:13.725Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Signal already kind of has this – you can change group permissions so that only admins can send messages, thus everyone who is a regular user is now a “read-only participant”. Of course, that means in order to be able to send messages, users would then have to be admin, which gives them additional group management controls, so it’s not exactly what you want.</p>",
