        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote group-volunteer_moderators\" data-username=\"Herohtar\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"65934\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/herohtar/48/43780_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Herohtar:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Of course, that means in order to be able to send messages, users would then have to be admin, which gives them additional group management controls, so it’s not exactly what you want.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>that could be achieved if some more granular version of the super-admin discussed in this thread gets implemented:</p><aside class=\"quote\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"22385\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/dragon/48/12305_2.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/admin-shouldnt-be-able-to-revoke-admin-title-of-the-group-creator/22385\">Admin shouldn't be able to revoke admin title of the group creator</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/feature-requests/17\"><span data-category-id=\"17\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #83B72A; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF;\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category \" title=\"Post your ideas here for new features and functionality for the Signal app.\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Feature Requests</span></span></a>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    Admin shouldn’t be able to revoke admin title of the group creator. On whatsapp is not possible, in signal it is. Why? I suggest to make it impossible \nA possible implementation could be this one: <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/admin-shouldnt-be-able-to-revoke-admin-title-of-the-group-creator/22385/2\" class=\"inline-onebox\">Admin shouldn't be able to revoke admin title of the group creator - #2 by ProactiveServices</a>\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n",
